node.text: Happy Father’s Day babe 💓🥺 I don’t have to sit here and elaborate how you are the best father to our son because it’s clear as water and everyone can see it! Our baby G is so lucky to have you as his role model and life guide, I hope our son turns out to be as great of a father as you one day. I couldn’t have picked anyone better to raise this little human with, we love you baby❤️ @vlexgalindo
